<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Review Import - Splitwise</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a> |
        <a href="/group/{{groupId}}">Back to group</a> |
        <a href="/group/{{groupId}}/import">Re-upload</a>
    </nav>
    <main>
        <h1>Review Import</h1>
        <p>Assign a payer for each row, then confirm to create the expenses. All expenses will be split equally among all group members.</p>

        <form method="post" action="/group/{{groupId}}/import/confirm">
            <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{csrfToken}}">
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Date</th>
                        <th>Description</th>
                        <th>Amount</th>
                        <th>Paid by</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each rows}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{date}}</td>
                        <td>{{description}}</td>
                        <td>{{amount}}</td>
                        <td>
                            <select name="payer_{{rowIndex}}" required>
                                {{#each ../members}}
                                <option value="{{id}}">{{username}}</option>
                                {{/each}}
                            </select>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <button type="submit">Confirm and create expenses</button>
        </form>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
